---
// BoomMap.astro — visual SVG map for /blog/puget-sound-construction-boom-map-2026
//
// County outlines derived from US Census 2010 Cartographic Boundary Files
// (1:5,000,000 scale), filtered to WA state code 53 + the four Puget Sound
// metro counties (Pierce 053, King 033, Snohomish 061, Kitsap 035), then
// projected to a viewBox via cosine-corrected equirectangular.
//
// Project marker positions are approximate (within ~2 miles).
//
// Usage:
//   import BoomMap from '../../components/BoomMap.astro';
//   <BoomMap />
